00:15:14.868 --> 00:15:17.037 align:center line:81%
with all the different clothing,

00:15:17.037 --> 00:15:18.830 align:center line:81%
seeing that made me feel Iike, okay,

00:15:18.830 --> 00:15:19.706 align:center line:81%
I have to be that

00:15:19.706 --> 00:15:21.708 align:center line:81%
because that's what New York is about,

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:24.002 align:center line:81%
