00:15:44.106 --> 00:15:46.358 align:center line:81%
Um... for others...

00:15:46.358 --> 00:15:49.111 align:center line:81%
just so that they would be happy.

00:15:49.319 --> 00:15:51.113 align:center line:81%
It felt like being an imposter.

00:15:51.113 --> 00:15:52.114 align:center line:81%
It wasn't my world,

00:15:52.114 --> 00:15:54.116 align:center line:81%
I was just living in it.

00:15:54.783 --> 00:15:56.952 align:center line:81%
