00:16:08.964 --> 00:16:10.966 align:center line:81%
and he wants you to be in that home.

00:16:11.216 --> 00:16:13.218 align:center line:81%
I felt a little tingly in my heart

00:16:13.218 --> 00:16:16.430 align:center line:81%
and it feels like a super, overpowering

00:16:16.722 --> 00:16:17.681 align:center line:81%
love.

00:16:20.767 --> 00:16:22.561 align:center line:81%
That little feeling of love,

00:16:22.561 --> 00:16:24.563 align:center line:81%
it changed my life forever.

00:16:28.275 --> 00:16:30.277 align:center line:81%
I felt loved,

00:16:30.402 --> 00:16:32.029 align:center line:81%
secure,

00:16:32.029 --> 00:16:33.655 align:center line:81%
all those things.

00:16:33.655 --> 00:16:36.116 align:center line:81%
But the main thing was the people-pleasing,

00:16:36.366 --> 00:16:37.284 align:center line:81%
completely stopped.

00:16:39.119 --> 00:16:40.287 align:center line:81%
I think that, now,

00:16:40.287 --> 00:16:42.664 align:center line:79%
the way that I connect 
with people is so pure.

00:16:42.664 --> 00:16:44.166 align:center line:81%
It comes from a place of love.

00:16:44.166 --> 00:16:45.917 align:center line:79%
Ice skating! 
- Here we go!

00:16:47.794 --> 00:16:49.671 align:center line:81%
I'm able to build

00:16:49.671 --> 00:16:51.506 align:center line:81%
honest, truthful relationships

00:16:51.506 --> 00:16:52.924 align:center line:81%
where I’m able to 

00:16:52.924 --> 00:16:54.092 align:center line:81%
actually put myself out there

00:16:54.092 --> 00:16:55.510 align:center line:81%
and be accepted 

00:16:55.510 --> 00:16:58.388 align:center line:81%
and loved, still being myself.

00:16:58.638 --> 00:17:00.265 align:center line:81%
I'm still very ordinary.

00:17:00.265 --> 00:17:01.850 align:center line:81%
I still love going out to eat.

00:17:01.850 --> 00:17:03.477 align:center line:81%
I love going shopping.

00:17:03.477 --> 00:17:05.479 align:center line:81%
I love doing my picnics in the park.

00:17:05.729 --> 00:17:07.731 align:center line:81%
But internally, I’m completely changed.

00:17:08.774 --> 00:17:10.734 align:center line:79%
There are nine million people 
in New York City,

00:17:10.734 --> 00:17:12.736 align:center line:81%
but God only made one Perla.

00:17:19.993 --> 00:17:21.286 align:center line:81%
If God exists,

00:17:21.286 --> 00:17:23.288 align:center line:79%
what would you ask?
– Mmm

00:17:23.288 --> 00:17:24.247 align:center line:81%
Umm...

